#: ../../B/BUAF.rst:9
msgid ""
"[abbreviation, from :samp:`alt.fan.warlord`\\] Big Ugly ASCII Font — a "
"special form of :ref:`ASCII-art`\\. Various programs exist for rendering "
"text strings into block, bloob, and pseudo-script fonts in cells between "
"four and six character cells on a side; this is smaller than the letters "
"generated by older :ref:`banner` (sense 2) programs. These are sometimes "
"used to render one's name in a :ref:`sig-block`\\, and are critically "
"referred to as BUAFs. See :ref:`warlording`\\."
msgstr ""
"[略語。\\ :samp:`alt.fan.warlord`\\ から]Big Ugly ASCII Font(大きく醜いASCIIフォント)——\\ "
":ref:`ASCII-art`\\ "
"の特殊な一形態。文字列を、一辺4〜6文字セル分のセル内のブロック体、ぶよぶよ体、擬似筆記体フォントに描画するプログラムがいくつか存在する。これは古い\\"
" :ref:`banner`\\ (語義2)プログラムが生成する文字より小さい。これらは\\ :ref:`sig-block`\\ "
"で自分の名前を描くのに使われることがあり、批判的にBUAFと呼ばれる。\\ :ref:`warlording`\\ を参照。"
